      section.guide-section.three-up
        i.point-icon.icon-lock 
        h3.point-title Security
        p Service Line Up was built with highest possible security in mind. Not only do we use 128 bit AES key SSL security throughout the site, we also use a secure up to date Microsoft SQL 2012 database with enhanced form protection against SQL injections and buffer overruns.
      section.guide-section.three-up
        i.point-icon.icon-credit 
        h3.point-title Integrated Credit Card Processing
        p When you sign up with our preferred merchant you gain the ability to use our system to its highest potential. You will be able to charge your customers credit cards directly through Service Line Up . Eliminate having to duplicate data in another system. With great rates, no contracts and no setup fee it is an easy choice.
      section.guide-section.three-up
        i.point-icon.icon-calendar 
        h3.point-title Scheduling
        p Easily do scheduling with our smart scheduler. See what days and times you have available and schedule customers quickly and easily. Once you schedule a customer on a recurring appointment the system will generate their appointment automatically so you know what your schedule looks like weeks in advance.
      section.guide-section.three-up
        i.point-icon.icon-coin 
        h3.point-title Payments
        p Get paid with the click of a button through Service Line Up. By signing up with our preferred merchant you gain the ability to do all your credit card processing directly through our system. Easily keep track of all payments that are due in one simple place. With the ability to sort or filter results, getting paid couldn&rsquo;t be easier.
      section.guide-section.three-up
        i.point-icon.icon-users 
        h3.point-title Customers / Contractors
        p Keep track of all your customers with the ability to make notes, store pertinent information about the customer and their appointments. All of your contractors will be easy to keep track of as well with Service Line Up. Knowing when they get paid and how they get paid is all in one place.
      section.guide-section.three-up
        i.point-icon.icon-stats 
        h3.point-title Reports
        p From Payroll to Appointment Reports, Service Line Up has it all. The reports are designed to give you as much information as possible. They have been field tested so we know what information you will need to get your contractors to their job on time with all the information they will need.
